data.description: Welcome to 6964 Roundleaf Dr, Jacksonville, FL 32258, where you will find a spectacular opportunity that you simply won't want to miss. This lovely home offers 1728 square feet of living space complete with 3 bedrooms, 2.5 bathrooms, and plenty of additional features. This home comes with Electric Forced air heating and Central cooling, stainless steal appliances and the lot size is 2,178 square feet with a Garage attached as well as a beautiful back patio overlooking the lake. This is a remarkable opportunity that you should take advantage of. Don't pass up this incredible chance - come and see this splendid home today! Please keep in mind we will give a credit for new carpets at closing.
